Perform quasi-likelihood F-test

qlf <- list()
for (i in 1:ncls){
  qlf[[i]] <- glmQLFTest(fit, contrast=contr[,i])
  qlf[[i]]$comparison <- paste0(levels(layer)[i], '_vs_others')
}
